snippet: General Motors Co's Cadillac aims to increase its global annual sales to over 500,000 cars by 2020, a senior executive said on Friday....

headline.print_headline: GM's Cadillac Aims to Increase Global Annual Sales to Over 500,000 by 2020: Senior Executive
headline.main: GM's Cadillac Aims to Increase Global Annual Sales to Over 500,000 by 2020: Senior Executive

lead_paragraph: General Motors Co's Cadillac aims to increase its global annual sales to over 500,000 cars by 2020, a senior executive said on Friday.
